PydgetsRFID README
==================

PydgetsRFID [1] is a tool to interface with the Phidgets Inc. RFID
kit. It wraps libphidgets [2] with ctypes [3] to communicate with the
hardware.

Copyright (C) 2005-2006 Jo Vermeulen <jo.vermeulen@uhasselt.be>

This software is licensed under the GPL, see COPYING for more
details.

Feedback is always welcome!

Dependencies
------------

PydgetsRFID requires:

* libphidgets
* Python
* ctypes (included by default as of Python 2.5)
* PyGTK (for the GUI)

----
[1] http://www.jozilla.be/software/pydgetsrfid
[2] http://libphidgets.alioth.debian.org/
[3] http://docs.python.org/lib/module-ctypes.html

